You all sat in silence for a while, watching the screen. What you see first is your childhood. They look like you and the memories are very familiar, but some slight variations of what you remember. You ask your companions, "Why are we watching this?" And the person on the right said , "It's so we can learn from our mistakes and not make them again." You did not reply and continued to watch in silence.
